َهِ","d":"l-lahi","e":"(of) Allah"},{"b":"7.2","c":"ثُمَّ","d":"thumma","e":"then"},{"b":"8.5","c":"مَاتُوا","d":"mātū","e":"died"},{"b":"9.4","c":"وَهُمْ","d":"wahum","e":"while they"},{"b":"10.0","c":"كُفَّارٌ","d":"kuffārun","e":"(were) disbelievers"},{"b":"11.8","c":"فَلَنْ","d":"falan","e":"never"},{"b":"13.2","c":"يَغْفِرَ","d":"yaghfira","e":"will Allah forgive"},{"b":"14","c":"اللَّهُ","d":"l-lahu","e":"will Allah forgive"},{"b":"14.8","c":"لَهُمْ","d":"lahum","e":"them"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, those who disbelieved and averted [people] from the path of Allah and then died while they were disbelievers - never will Allah forgive them."}},"35":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","c":"فَلَا","d":"falā","e":"So (do) not"},{"b":"0.64","c":"تَهِنُوا","d":"tahinū","e":"weaken"},{"b":"1.5","c":"وَتَدْعُوا","d":"watadʿū","e":"and call"},{"b":"4.0","c":"إِلَى","d":"ilā","e":"for"},{"b":"4.3","c":"السَّلْمِ","d":"l-salmi","e":"peace"},{"b":"5.2","c":"وَأَنْتُمُ","d":"wa-antumu","e":"while you"},{"b":"6.8","c":"الْأَعْلَوْنَ","d":"l-aʿlawna","e":"(are) superior"},{"b":"8.0","c":"وَاللَّهُ","d":"wal-lahu","e":"and Allah"},{"b":"9.2","c":"مَعَكُمْ","d":"maʿakum","e":"(is) with you"},{"b":"10.","c":"وَلَنْ","d":"walan","e":"and never"},{"b":"11.1","c":"يَتِرَكُمْ","d":"yatirakum","e":"will deprive you"},{"b":"12.1","c":"أَعْمَالَكُمْ","d":"aʿmālakum","e":"(of) your deeds"}],"a":{"g":"So do not weaken and call for peace while you are superior; and Allah is with you and will never deprive you of [the reward of] your deeds."}},"36":{"w":[{"b":"0.07","c":"إِنَّمَا","d":"innamā","e":"Only"},{"b":"1.6","c":"الْحَيَوةُ","d":"l-ḥayatu","e":"the life"},{"b":"2.8","c":"الدُّنْيَا","d":"l-dun'yā","e":"(of) the world"},{"b":"3.8","c":"لَعِبٌ","d":"laʿibun","e":"(is) play"},{"b":"4.6","c":"وَلَهْوٌ","d":"walahwun","e":"and amusement"},{"b":"6.9","c":"وَإِنْ","d":"wa-in","e":"And if"},{"b":"8.3","c":"تُؤْمِنُوا","d":"tu'minū","e":"you believe"},{"b":"9.4","c":"وَتَتَّقُوا","d":"watattaqū","e":"and fear (Alla